{"tid":1017912,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜通宵夜貓唔願訓tg grp(新谷收人呀喂)","createTime":"2019-02-11T20:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T09:20:22.000Z","uid":62147,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2479f4c7e720458524b653c94df085360ad1a791","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T20:46:17.000Z","msg":"一睇個谷名就知係專比夜貓架啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔理你夜訓又好，唔訓又好，總之專係夜晚先開始活動既你就岩哂啦<br />\n夜晚搵唔到人陪？呢到有一班夜貓陪住你，快啲入黎一齊尻下fing下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個谷新開既，所以唔驚咩老屎忽小圈子，最緊要多啲出聲，幫手搞旺個場呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n谷聚呢層就緊係有啦，成班夜貓出黎咁就緊係夜晚搵啲野玩，飲酒唱k宵夜踩板坐海旁...總之你諗到夜晚可以做既野就可以出聲約聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然唔排除大家熟咗都可以朝早活動下其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n年齡主要都係30歲樓下，成班後生仔女無無聊聊尻下開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n狗公貓公呢啲唔多講啦，唔好搞到咁出面，咁大個人明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之你夠尻，夠夜訓，就入黎一齊fing下啦，填link啦baby<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/h3XPGjfROIiGPnLQ2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fh3XPGjfROIiGPnLQ2&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1wx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=a0bc5dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/h3XPGjfROIiGPnLQ2</a>"},{"pid":"559a7c350165a22d1285bf893ae03240e9f46d1b","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T21:51:20.000Z","msg":"推推佢"},{"pid":"6412930b1a908704f5d0f663c765ddb12cb9f39f","tid":1017912,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T21:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c354d444b831a14bbe0bc398c5a63ce9661296","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6412930b1a908704f5d0f663c765ddb12cb9f39f","tid":1017912,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T21:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T00:03:03.000Z","msg":"感謝推post喔"},{"pid":"f6d1fec790eb1e529426407d02782a4aba14de3c","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"0a9e981561539ce553198e4509d4b61eb28514b9","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"105d6a1a8e41d77a6ecdac0d6b6cc03298f4b9e1","tid":1017912,"uid":17781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9e981561539ce553198e4509d4b61eb28514b9","tid":1017912,"uid":62147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"推推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2